        Spade-BDI
        =========
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/spade_bdi.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/spade
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/spade_bdi.svg
